This directory contains data files used for the maximum likelihood
estimation with quarterly data in
                                                                                
    Business Cycle Accounting
    Staff Report 328
    by V.V. Chari, Patrick Kehoe, and Ellen McGrattan
                                                                                
For full details, see the appendix in directory ./tex.
                                                                                
FILE             DESCRIPTION
------------     ----------------------------------------------------
Hours.pdf        Prescott, Ueberfeldt, and Cociuba (2005) 
Hours.xls        Data for constructing hours and productivity series in PUC.
hours.dat        2 columns from Hours.xls
atab10d.pdf      Flow of Funds Table F10, page from book
atab10d.dat      Flow of Funds Table F10 data
btab100d.pdf     Flow of Funds Table L100, page from book
btab100d.dat     Flow of Funds Table L100 data
nipa###.doc      NIPA table corresponding to ###, description
nipa###.dat      NIPA table corresponding to ###, raw data

Ellen McGrattan
February 2005
